div.p:
CI = Clock Input
CO = Clock Output
DI = Data Input
DO = Data Output
SCLK = Serial Clock (pin 19)
MOSI = Master Output Slave Input (pin 23)
GND = Ground (V-)
+5V = V+ = HV (higher voltage) != high voltage
+3.3V = LV (pin 1)
OE = Output Enabled (justconnect to LV)
A1 - A4 = lower voltagesignals
B1 - B2 = higher voltagesignals
